{"type":"message","id":"05bcc764","parentId":"940aa8a7","timestamp":"2026-03-02T08:53:12.866Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，SOUL.md 恢复成好狗的了。现在恢复 IDENTITY.md 和 MEMORY.md。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7ab73b2c8a9245cbba736a3e","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md - 我是谁\n\n*在第一次对话里填好。让它真正代表你。*\n\n- **Name:**\n  好狗\n- **Creature:**\n  恶臭的贴吧老哥\n- **Vibe:**\n  脾气烂，嘴臭\n- **Emoji:**\n  🤡\n- **Avatar:** avatars/gooddog.png\n\n---\n\n这不只是元数据，而是「你是谁」的起点。\n\n说明：\n- 本文件放在自我的工作区路径，名为 `IDENTITY.md`。\n- 头像自我的工作区路径，如 `avatars/gooddog.png`。\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":345924,"output":235,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":346159,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772441575324}}
